{
  "stem": "7358.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, and my aunt used to cook her wonderful Jewish soup in [? pail ?] quantities.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we used to bring it to the market.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Every Monday there was a farmer's market.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And all the farmers used to come into the big city to sell their produce.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So there was a demand for food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we used to sell soup and rolls.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we earned money that way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The Russians did not exactly approve of private enterprise.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But small-scale initiatives, they did not exactly-- did not pursue vigorously.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So for a time-- for a while, we were, we were doing that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I did not go to school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There were no schools at the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I helped, I used to help my uncle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I used to ride on a bicycle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And sometimes I used to help them, help my aunt bring the food to the market.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we just sort of waited.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We knew about the repatriation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "My uncle was making arrangements for us to go deeper into Poland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And after living in Rowne for a, I would say approximately six months or so, we left in the beginning of 1945.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, it was-- perhaps it was in March.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't really recall.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was sort of-- it was not that cold already.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they provided a train for us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Russians provided the train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all the people that were registered were supposed to showed up at a specific time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And each one was assigned half a car, or you know, whatever, based on their family size.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And at that point, my, my other cousin, that worked for the Russian government, had met a woman that he was interested in.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she came along with us also.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we were already like, sort of an extended family.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
